SplashNext !Japan
Set STBJapan$Path <Obey$Dir>.

Set Japan$Path STBJapan:Resources.Japan.
Set JapanIME$Path STBJapan:Resources.JapanIME.
Set JapanIME$Module STBJapan:Modules.JapanIME

RMCheck InternationalIME 0.02 IntIME
RMEnsure Japan 0.37 RMLoad STBJapan:Modules.Japan
If "<STB$Territory>"="Japan" Then RMEnsure JapanIME 0.20 RMLoad STBJapan:Modules.JapanIME

TerrFont Japan MaruGothic MaruGothic.Medium
